Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:06.07,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mini戰國basara2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.30,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對決！月夜的片倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:19.32,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒人趁著夜色逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:26.94,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反 最近儘是一群趁著夜色溜進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.09,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.24,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.45,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:32.64,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:33.91,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.91,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜又會有誰 來幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:44.43,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以好好期待一下哦 片倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.94,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹中半兵衛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:51.70,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就知道是我 這可是個吉兆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:53.72,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.33,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是你的遊樂場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.60,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無論如何也想讓你成為豐臣家的一分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.48,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我带了他來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:05.58,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.02,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豐臣秀吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.77,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也會為秀吉而陶醉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:28.97,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到他這種壓倒眾生的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.67,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.64,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.01,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下水脈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.24,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.20,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 片倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:14.67,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是秀吉的力量 豐臣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.98,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當能幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.96,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的水田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.11,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連水都能引來 太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.84,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一瞬間就能採摘完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:34.96,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這麼強的力量 也難怪你會迷上他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.87,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.94,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀吉的力量是為了讓這個國家興盛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.57,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 讓這個國家的農作物豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.29,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:52.49,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 片倉君已經被迷得神魂顛倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.53,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當你已降伏在秀吉座前了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:00.92,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說降伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.22,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了龍之右目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.62,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.94,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光合作用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.36,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.42,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我片倉小十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:42.26,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論收成有多麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.05,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會捨棄一顆菜的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.60,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.54,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子你得一直吃蔬菜了哦
